 confirm the\nlimitations of the standard estimation method in scenarios of high additive\nnoise and MDL/MDG, and indicate the correction factor as a possible solution in\npractical SDM scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2020 12:52:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-08"}
