subset of the labels in the second graph are known prior to matching.\nIn this scenario, in addition to obtaining necessary and sufficient conditions\nfor successful matching, a polytime matching algorithm is proposed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 Aug 2020 18:02:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2021 03:45:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
